HEADWORD: Suscipient
<hw>Sus*cip"i*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who takes or admits; one
who receives.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suscitability</ent>⟦br⟧
